The paper discusses the security of machine learning based biometric authentication systems, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also uses machine learning classifiers and biometric modalities, which are commonly studied in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) research. Additionally, the paper proposes mitigation techniques, which involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and multimedia (cs.MM) techniques.
